OL,3,CResidents to return home after 40ft
OL,4,Csinkhole appeared in street
OL,6,FA local council says residents will be
OL,7,Fable to return home for Christmas
OL,8,Fafter a giant sinkhole appeared
OL,9,Foutside homes in Merthyr Tydfil on
OL,10,FSunday, 1 December.
OL,12,FThe 40ft cavity, which increased in
OL,13,Fsize last week, first appeared outside
OL,14,Fhomes on Nant Morlais, due to a
OL,15,Fcollapsed culvert following Storm Bert
OL,16,Fsix days earlier.
