OL,3,CResidents to return home after 40ft
OL,4,Csinkhole appeared in street
OL,6,FThirty homes were evacuated meaning
OL,7,Fresidents were forced into hotels and
OL,8,FAirbnbs, only allowed to return to
OL,9,Ftheir properties to retrieve clothing
OL,10,Fand certain other items.
OL,12,FToday, Merthyr Tydfil County Borough
OL,13,FCouncil began filling the void with
OL,14,Frocks in order to allow residents home
OL,15,Fas soon as possible.
OL,17,FThe local authority confirmed some
OL,18,Fresidents will be able to return as
OL,19,Fsoon as today, whilst others may have
OL,20,Fto wait until next week.
