OL,6,FHowever, the work currently being
OL,7,Fconducted is a temporary fix and more
OL,8,Fwill have to be done in the new year
OL,9,Fto ensure a permanent solution.
OL,11,FThe local authority confirmed that a
OL,12,F6ft diameter pipe, 9 meters long, has
OL,13,Fbeen placed in the sinkhole. It will
OL,14,Fact as as an overflow pipe to catch
OL,15,Fexcess water if pumps can't cope with
OL,16,Fthe flow.
OL,18,FThe hole will be filled temporarily,
OL,19,Fwith a design team constructing and
OL,20,Fimplementing a permanent and safe
OL,21,Fstructure in the new year.
