OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, resident Meurig
OL,7,FPrice said: "It's not a pleasant thing
OL,8,Fto do, leaving your house, locking up
OL,9,Fand not knowing when you're going to
OL,10,Fcome back. Fortunately we've been
OL,11,Flucky and able to stay with my
OL,12,Fdaughter.
OL,14,F"The local authority have been
OL,15,Fbrilliant at keeping in touch. Every
OL,16,Fday we've had a phone call keeping us
OL,17,Fup to date, so we've been counting
OL,18,Fdown the days."
