OL,6,FHe added: "We attended a meeting last
OL,7,Fnight and we were given assurances
OL,8,Fthat said it is safer now than it has
OL,9,Fever been, so hopefully the remedial
OL,10,Fwork they do after Christmas will put
OL,11,Fit back to right then and hopefully
OL,12,Fget everything back to normal."
OL,14,FBrent Carter, leader of Merthyr Tydfil
OL,15,FCounty Borough Council, said: "We've
OL,16,Fhad some really positive news, houses
OL,17,F1-7 have been allowed back home today,
OL,18,Fthey've had the all clear from Welsh
OL,19,FWater. So, they started moving in
OL,20,Fwhich is great news.
