OL,3,CResidents to return home after 40ft
OL,4,Csinkhole appeared in street
OL,6,F"We have work starting too. We've had
OL,7,Fstone delivered early this morning,
OL,8,Fand will be delivered all through the
OL,9,Fday. We're waiting for a conveyer belt
OL,10,Fto come in and the hole will start to
OL,11,Fbe filled up with stone to make it a
OL,12,Fsafe temporary base. And hopefully
OL,13,Fthen, by the middle of next week,
OL,14,Feverybody will be able to move back
OL,15,Finto their homes for Christmas, which
OL,16,Fis fantastic news."
OL,18,FMr Carter praised the residents as
OL,19,F"brilliant" despite it having been "a
OL,20,Ftraumatic experience" for them.
